message:
Aisha Khairat Al-shater from #Egypt :

Internal threats using live fire to intimidate people to not go down today ....And what you used before ... Not afraid of threats.God willing ... Descend to fields ... Break the constraint. I demand to the martyrs. We will recover. ... We were taught to ... Not pandering or coup ... Either victory or martyrdom. Perhaps a Salve from the oppression of the people and meet with the Valentines.
